        FROM [AbpSettings] AS [a]
        WHERE [a].[Name] = @__name_0 AND [a].[TenantId] IS NULL AND [a].[UserId] IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

        WHERE [a].[Name] = @__name_0 AND [a].[TenantId] IS NULL AND [a].[UserId] IS NULL) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

    SELECT TOP(1) [e].[Id], [e].[Grade], [e].[ExpectedTotalAmount], [e].[FullAmountWith5PercentDiscount], [e].[FullAmountDueDate]
    FROM [EducationalFeePlans] AS [e]
    WHERE [e].[Grade] = @__student_Grade_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [EducationalInstallments] AS [e0] ON [t].[Id] = [e0].[EducationalFeePlanId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]

FROM [StudentEducationalPayments] AS [s]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[RoleId] = [t0].[Id]
WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2) AND [a].[UserId] = @__user_Id_0

) AS [t0] ON [t].[RoleId] = [t0].[Id]
WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2) AND [a].[UserId] = @__user_Id_0

SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[BusFeePlanId], [s].[Notes], [s].[Status], [s].[StudentId], [s].[SubscriptionDate], [s0].[Id], [s0].[Grade], [s0].[MobileNumber], [s0].[Name], [s0].[PreviousAmount], [s0].[Status], [s0].[StudentId], [b].[Id], [b].[ExpectedTotalAmount], [b].[FullAmountDueDate], [b].[FullAmountWith5PercentDiscount], [b].[Line]
FROM [StudentBusSubscriptions] AS [s]
